Package task6.ingredient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    A_Ingredient
    Defines the shared elements of an ingredient in the form of a decorator that may wrap another ingredient recursively.
    A_IngredientBase
    Defines the shared elements of base ingredients that can have extra ingredients added to them.
    A_IngredientExtra
    Defines the shared elements of extra ingredients to be added to a base ingredient or other extra ingredients.
    IngredientBaseCoffeeDecaf
    Defines decaffeinated coffee as a base ingredient that can have extra ingredients added to it.
    IngredientBaseCoffeeRegular
    Defines regular coffee as a base ingredient that can have extra ingredients added to it.
    IngredientExtraCream
    Defines cream as an extra ingredient to be added to a base or extra ingredient.
    IngredientExtraMilk
    Defines milk as an extra ingredient to be added to a base or extra ingredient.
    IngredientExtraSugar
    Defines sugar as an extra ingredient to be added to a base or extra ingredient.
